{"tid":2125107,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"匈國獨媒總辭撐總編 萬人聲援","createTime":"2020-07-26T03:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T04:33:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2997537ca5e151b09ec7103808498ff8647e0053","tid":2125107,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:07:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200726/XHYTIZ7SWK5WLLJIFV3A6MBEW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200726%2FXHYTIZ7SWK5WLLJIFV3A6MBEW4%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLn%2B2WlZ9u1jPvSwBLlLsdxY%3D&h=d2ab1211\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200726%2FXHYTIZ7SWK5WLLJIFV3A6MBEW4%2F&h=b46ccd3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200726/XHYTIZ7SWK5WLLJIFV3A6MBEW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n匈國獨媒總辭撐總編 萬人聲援<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZcFavQ0lrEh0q4Yuh6adIXxERD8=/640x425/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UGLSJVAWJ6DACDPEUGS5M2ER5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZcFavQ0lrEh0q4Yuh6adIXxERD8%3D%2F640x425%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUGLSJVAWJ6DACDPEUGS5M2ER5E.jpg&h=fa3d40db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n匈牙利撐新聞自由示威者前晚齊亮手機當燭光。路透社<br />\n<br />\n匈牙利最大獨立媒體Index.hu幾乎所有員工集體辭職，抗議管理層在親政府勢力的壓力下辭退總編輯達爾（Szabolcs Dull），近萬名示威者其後上街聲援，譴責奧爾班政府打壓新聞自由。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：執法人員變打手 特朗普遭譴責<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遭親政府勢力打壓<br />\n<br />\n參與總辭的包括三名高級編輯和80多名記者，他們前日在公開信宣佈「編輯委員會認為獨立運作的條件已不存在，已經辭職」。決定總辭的副編輯芒克狠批高層的做法已越過紅線，又透露很多員工前日離開辦公室時都感觸落淚。<br />\n<br />\n數小時後，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nIndex.hu每日有近200萬讀者，被認為是匈牙利最後一間獨立媒體。其新聞自由風波可追溯至今年3月，當時親奧爾班富商華斯奇利買入了一間Index.hu依賴的廣告中介公司一半股權，控制了Index.hu的收入，達爾不久後已將Index.hu的自由指標由「獨立」下調至危險。至上周三，管理層辭退了達爾，並拒絕按編採人員要求讓他復職，觸發這次事件。<br />\n<br />\n奧爾班所屬政黨青民盟過往亦被指以類似手法控制媒體，如將Origo轉為親政府媒體和令左傾的《人民自由報》停刊，歐盟曾多次表示關注。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/路透社"},{"pid":"a5ca5d26eacb4b18523ba9ba9d596cb7d40557ee","tid":2125107,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2015/02/04/984021_a809eed4f448c98ca879c7f5f13faa96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2015%2F02%2F04%2F984021_a809eed4f448c98ca879c7f5f13faa96.jpg&h=c92485ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34a83df72b07107946ab5b80f35f8224ed7e4df7","tid":2125107,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:37:07.000Z","msg":"講奶共匈牙利一定係第一名"},{"pid":"ebeba2e05069fea42991fdd4b5d2fbf0a81677f2","tid":2125107,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報 會是香港的匈牙利翻版嗎 ？"},{"pid":"255f42545046018c79607dab7ee30e1ccf7ae508","tid":2125107,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"明報，港台"},{"pid":"fc8645dfd25ff2127ebf75fc2a88a08b66cb86ff","tid":2125107,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"匈牙利，塞爾維亞，蒙特內哥羅東歐三國出名近年獨裁化，被中俄直接影響，匈牙利由民主改革先驅變到今時今日支那化"},{"pid":"ba7e4f6506c4cc2d931052948a3b35fc07272638","tid":2125107,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"人民同政權要分開"}]}